  "text": "This paper gives our preferred approach to providing tool support for consistency checking using so-called 'uniform properties' [CITATION_1] . It makes use of an existing PVS embedding of the traces model of CSP, and shows how these properties need to be extended for CSP B sequences of operation calls (which are akin to traces but with state updates).",
